  "body": "As per our discussion in the #zeppelin_os channel on Slack, \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/mochajs/mocha/wiki/Shared-Behaviours\r\n\r\nShared Behaviours would enable a much more flexible and developer friendly testing experience. \r\n\r\nExisting test coverage of dependant contracts would be importable into the test cases being generated for new contracts. \r\n\r\nThis would greatly improve the test development experience for simple and complex contracts and bring a significant level of assurance to changes/emerging patterns and visibility into breaking issues. \r\n\r\n",
